                      "gap": 10,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "sxyjU",
                          "fill": "$text-mid",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "你的优势在于回应感、共情力和自然建立连接的能力。你能用一种不冒犯、不压迫的方式，把温度慢慢带进关系里。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.85,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                          "fontSize": "$fs-body",
                          "fontWeight": "normal",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.3
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "zmSG8",
                          "fill": "$text-mid",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "需要留意的是，如果你总是顺着关系流动，却很少明确表达自己的需求，别人可能会感受到你的温暖，却不一定真正知道你也需要被回应。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.85,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                          "fontSize": "$fs-body",
                          "fontWeight": "normal",
                          "letterSpacing": 0.3
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
